The paper deals with training-based transmission over MIMO channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The analysis of achievable rates and energy efficiency involves statistical inference (cs.SI) and networked systems (cs.NI). The investigation of successive decoding receivers also falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
